@startuml
title 生命周期工作流 - 架构图
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

component "LifecycleWorkflow" as Workflow
rectangle "ConfigLoader" as Config
rectangle "订阅初始化" as Subscription
rectangle "指标 / 信号服务" as SignalServices
rectangle "选约 / 定价 / 风控 /\n仓位服务" as DecisionServices
rectangle "聚合根" as Aggregates
rectangle "Gateway 组" as Gateways
rectangle "持久化 / 监控" as Persistence
rectangle "BarPipeline" as BarPipeline
rectangle "Feishu 告警" as Alert
rectangle "History / OMS 恢复" as Recovery

Workflow --> Config : 读取配置
Workflow --> Subscription : 初始化订阅模式
Workflow --> SignalServices : 构建策略内核服务
Workflow --> DecisionServices : 构建可选领域服务
Workflow --> Aggregates : 初始化 / 恢复
Workflow --> Gateways : 构建市场接入
Workflow --> Persistence : 创建仓储、autosave、monitor
Workflow --> BarPipeline : 构建 K 线聚合
Workflow --> Alert : 注册 / 注销事件处理器
Workflow --> Recovery : 回测预热或实盘恢复
@enduml
